@startuml
title FaceUiState – State Machine

[*] --> Idle

Idle    --> Loading    : scanner opened / camera init

Loading --> Detection  : camera ready

' ─── Detection sub-states (real-time feedback loop) ───────────────
state Detection {
  [*]          --> NoFace

  NoFace       --> FaceDetected   : face appears
  FaceDetected --> NoFace         : face lost

  FaceDetected --> MultipleFaces  : >1 face detected
  MultipleFaces --> FaceDetected  : single face again

  FaceDetected --> MoveCloser     : face too small
  FaceDetected --> CenterFace     : face off-center
  FaceDetected --> LookStraight   : head rotation > 12°
  FaceDetected --> HoldStill      : movement too fast
  FaceDetected --> ImproveFocus   : frame blurry
  FaceDetected --> EyesNotOpen    : eyes closed / covered
  FaceDetected --> WearingGlasses : glasses detected
  FaceDetected --> WearingHat     : hat detected
  FaceDetected --> SpoofDetected  : passive liveness failed

  MoveCloser    --> FaceDetected
  CenterFace    --> FaceDetected
  LookStraight  --> FaceDetected
  HoldStill     --> FaceDetected
  ImproveFocus  --> FaceDetected
  EyesNotOpen   --> FaceDetected
  WearingGlasses --> FaceDetected
  WearingHat    --> FaceDetected
  SpoofDetected --> FaceDetected
}

Detection --> Loading : 4 quality frames captured\n→ embedding computation begins

' ─── Enroll branch ────────────────────────────────────────────────
state "Enroll Flow" as EnrollFlow {
  [*]              --> CaptureProcessed
  CaptureProcessed --> FullNameConflict  : name taken or < 3 chars
  FullNameConflict --> CaptureProcessed  : user corrects input
  CaptureProcessed --> Completed         : valid name → saved to DB
}

' ─── Verify branch ────────────────────────────────────────────────
state "Verify Flow" as VerifyFlow {
  [*]     --> Matching
  Matching --> Verified           : best cosine score >= 0.82
  Matching --> VerificationFailed : best cosine score < 0.82
}

Loading --> EnrollFlow  : ENROLL mode – embedding ready
Loading --> VerifyFlow  : VERIFY mode – embedding ready

EnrollFlow --> [*] : Completed
VerifyFlow --> [*]

Loading   --> Error : exception
Detection --> Error : exception
Error     --> [*]

@enduml
